page.title: 03Family Life
page.content: A typical day for me would be to get up at about 7.00 and switch the television on to watch Popeye at 7.25 on T.V.A.M. I get out of bed at 7.30, get dressed and go and feed the guinea pigs. I have two, Salt and Pepper. I go to school at about 8.35 although school doesn't start until 8.45. Play times come at 10.30 and 2.25. Dinner time is from 12.00 to 1.15. We leave school at about 3.30. When I get home on Mondays I go to piano lessons. From 7.00 to 9.00 on Mondays I go to Guides at Killingholme.
